title: Diamond Rush from Plat3+ (LF DuoQ Partner)
body:
Hi,
I am looking for a DuoQ Partner for a Diamond rush. I am on vacation right now so I can play all day/night long! You should be around Platin3 too.
My main role is ADC/Jungle - you can play any role you want ; I prefer you to be Mid/Jungle tho
Just add me in-game (IGN: Wizzh) and we can play right after.
